markdownRemark.html: Yes. They often have simple pious woodcuts or (less frequently) classroom scenes. They are frightfully rare, however, and I do not have an example I can show you in a photo. Some sense of the genre may be had by looking at the cuts reproduced in Malaguzzi, cited below.
